{
  "stem": "25348.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I spoke Polish without an accent-- and I think a lot of Jewish people exposed themselves, particularly those whose language was not Polish at home-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I could get out of the ghetto and to occasionally arrange some food for Mother and I.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, go on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's very hard to measure distances from the perception of a 14-year-old in Poland with our distances in Australia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've spent most of my life here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I would say it was like going from another suburb, from one suburb to another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had lost all contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether he was trapped-- he and my brothers were trapped at the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I heard different versions from people, some from Lwow, whom I met after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sort of getting away from the chronology, but I have to tell you this, that someone told me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lwow had one of its biggest working camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was called Janowska, spelled with a J.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Janowska-- J-A-N-O-W-S-K-A.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was one version of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another version of it was-- and that is a fact that this happened, whether any of my male members of the family were there, I will never know for sure.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They hounded all the Jews into the Jewish-- it was called the Temple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was probably a reform-- more of a reform synagogue and the largest one in Melbourne-- a very prominent one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they, they burned it to the ground while the Jews were inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was the other version of how my peoples did not survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
